snippet.title: Dark Deception: Monsters & Mortals DLC Showcase 02 - SILENT HILL | Hosted by SuperHorrorBro
snippet.description:
Wishlist the Monsters & Mortals: Silent Hill  DLC on Steam! It launches on March 23rd!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1508810/Monsters__Mortals__Silent_Hill/
Dark Deception: Monsters & Mortals is available on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1266690/Dark_Deception_Monsters__Mortals

Follow SuperHorrorBro's channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChL4WU9YLlxXXNSwlzM1-7g

Video edited by Mike Bambridge (SuperHorrorBro)
Music composed by Daniel Dombrowsky
(Original Claw Finger track composed by Akira Yamaoka)
